donald e buz lukens failed to conduct himself at all times in a 
manner which reflects creditably on the house of representatives 
it notes that house members in order to perform their 
constitutional duties must conduct themselves with integrity and 
that house rules require conduct which will not bring disrepute on 
the institution 
michel said the gop will live up to its constitutional obligation 
to police its own members no matter how distasteful or painful 
