pointe and judy tyrus who will dance the lead on june 25 was 
perky and refreshing in her pas de deux with augustus van heerden 
during its new york run through july 2 the dance theater of 
harlem will perform works from its repertoire including 
balanchines allegro brillante mitchells holberg suite and 
glen tetleys voluntaries the company also will premiere works 
by nijinska 
