<TEXT>
paramount communications inc moved today to get 
a court order blocking time incs proposed 14 billion acquisition 
of warner communications inc 
paramount an entertainment and publishing concern has launched 
its own 107 billion offer for time a leading magazine publisher 
and cable operator 
time has rejected paramounts bid 
in trading today on the new york stock exchange time was up 3 a 
share to 15550 time had fallen more than 18 a share over the 
past three trading days since it launched its bid for warner and 
rejected paramounts offer 
warner was down 12 cents a share at 5937 at midday while 
