goods are cheaper and even if you add in the shipping charges its 
still cheaper 
since halls company was established in 1981 it has produced 
chicken and dumplings chicken pot pies pork barbecue and such 
frozen rice dishes such as seafood and catfish gumbos 
in 1987 ramph joined nitto food products ltd a leading japanese 
food manufacturer and nozaki america inc a japanese trading 
company in forming georgia pro foods inc 
nitto sent hideo saga a consultant for a japanese company with 
which ramph markets the usmade frozen dinners to savannah to 
